[{"id":"51b70e6e63443003c8c1935230bb9c51","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: OFFER TO PURCHASE YOUR 2007 SK76++ sn 760667","date":"2008-05-09T19:27:28.000Z","formatted_date":"May 9, 2008","formatted_time":"7:27 PM","body":" \n\n \n\nFrom: Sean J. Lancaster [mailto:slancaster@bristolassociates.com] \nSent: Friday, May 09, 2008 3:27 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff; Darren Indyke; lvjet@aol.com\nCc: lvjet@aol.com\nSubject: FW: OFFER TO PURCHASE YOUR 2007 SK76++ sn 760667\n\n \n\nFor Mr. E please.\n\n \n\nThis is an offer from the Brazilians again.  Mr. Oliveria has suggested\nthat he would pay $12.6.  He does not expect a response today an\nunderstands the owner may not even see the offer until Monday.  I would\nsuggest if we decided to respond we draft a more formal Letter of\nIntent/Purchase Agreement with much stronger language.  \n\n \n\nI have also been told that we might see an offer next week from Wayne\nHuizenga next week.  \n\n \n\nBest regards \n\n \n\n \n\n\nSean J. Lancaster\n\nBristol Associates Inc.\n\n)+1-540-665-5135 direct\n\n(+1-202-682-4000 ext 1130 Main Office\n\n)+1-540-533-8183 Mobile\n\n4+1-540-301-0050 FAX\n\n* slancaster@bristolassociates.com\n<mailto:%20slancaster@bristolassociates.com> \n\n: www.bristolassociates.com <http://www.bristolassociates.com/>  \n\n \n\nThis message may contain confidential and/or legally privileged\ninformation.  If you are not the intended recipient of the message,\nplease destroy it. Any unauthorized dissemination, distribution or\ncopying of the material in this message, and any attachments to the\nmessage, is strictly forbidden. (c) 2008 all rights reserved.\n\n \n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: ceo@planaer.com.br [mailto:ceo@planaer.com.br] \nSent: Friday, May 09, 2008 2:52 PM\nTo: slancaster@bristolassociates.com\nSubject: OFFER TO PURCHASE YOUR 2007 SK76++ sn 760667\n\n \n\nDear  Sean,\n\n \n\nI have the following offer to purchase for this helicopter sn 760667: \n\n \n\n1. The helicopter shall be delivered in USA, with the FAA  C of A export\ncertificate to Brazil or to Venezuela ( to be advised) \n\n \n\n2. On the price shall be included the SK76++ initial course, in the\nFlight Safety School. Courses for 2 Pilots + 2 mechanics ( at your\ncosts)\n\n \n\n3. Our offer is U$ 12.3Million.\n\n \n\n4. If you accept that we can formalize and fax an OFFER TO PURCHASE with\na U$ 150K in IATS- Insured Aircraft Title Service, USA,  escrow\nrefundable deposit,  to retire the helicopter from the market and\nschedulle the acft. visit and the pre-purchase inspection.\n\n \n\nWe also need your Aircraft Purchase Agreement draft to be analised and\napproved by our attorneys\n\n \n\nThis offer is valid until may 12, 2008 16:00hs local time.\n\n \n\nSincerely\n\n \n\nJose A. Lins Oliveira     \nCEO\nPLANAER-Aviation Trade Brazil\nPh 55-11-3476 9951  // Cel.  55-11-9192 9887\nFax 55-11-5016 3860  \nwww.planaer.com.br\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n\t----- Original Message ----- \n\n\tFrom: Sean J. Lancaster\n<mailto:slancaster@bristolassociates.com>  \n\n\tTo: 'Jose Olivera' <mailto:joselins@globo.com>  ; 'Jose Olivera'\n<mailto:ceo@planaer.com.br>  \n\n\tSent: Friday, May 09, 2008 12:48 PM\n\n\t \n\n\t \n\n\t \n\n\tBest regards \n\n\t \n\n\t\n\n\n\tSean J. Lancaster\n\n\tBristol Associates Inc.\n\n\t)+1-540-665-5135 direct\n\n\t(+1-202-682-4000 ext 1130 Main Office\n\n\t)+1-540-533-8183 Mobile\n\n\t4+1-540-301-0050 FAX\n\n\t* slancaster@bristolassociates.com\n<mailto:slancaster@bristolassociates.com> \n\n\t: www.bristolassociates.com \n\n\t \n\n\tThis message may contain confidential and/or legally privileged\ninformation.  If you are not the intended recipient of the message,\nplease destroy it. Any unauthorized dissemination, distribution or\ncopying of the material in this message, and any attachments to the\nmessage, is strictly forbidden. (c) 2008 all rights r